</emphasis>
Like female except lower half of front with dense, long, golden setae, apical ventrite entire, broadly and weakly rounded; 
<quantity id="11404E997779C32755E24E16543ADF56" box="[499,584,1124,1145]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.75" pageId="1" pageNumber="222" unit="mm" value="4.75">4.75 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity id="11404E997779C32754864E0C5682DFBC" box="[151,240,1150,1171]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.3" pageId="1" pageNumber="222" unit="mm" value="2.3">2.30 mm</quantity>
wide; genitalia 
<quantity id="11404E997779C32755824E0C5799DFBC" box="[403,491,1150,1171]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" pageId="1" pageNumber="222" unit="mm" value="1.25">1.25 mm</quantity>
long, parallelsided at base with rounded transparent lobes for apical 
<quantity id="11404E997779C32754C94EC1575CDFE7" box="[216,302,1203,1224]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="222" unit="mm" value="0.2">0.20 mm</quantity>
of parameres.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
